Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.15,0:00:39.66,song2r,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}сердце хочет любви
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.15,0:00:39.66,song1r,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}yume ni aru aiji dake ni wa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.91,0:00:46.63,song2r,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}самой большой на свете
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.91,0:00:46.63,song1r,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}nani yori mo kagayaite
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.71,0:00:52.84,song2r,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}я ни о чём не жалею
